#### PR description:

The function was noticed to cause link problems because of multiple definitions in https://github.com/cms-sw/cmsdist/pull/6027. The function is indeed missing "inline" keyword, but the body looked complex-enough to be moved out of line.

`testDefaultModuleLabel` unit test runs.
title: Move edm::defaultModuleLabel() body out-of-line
